line_1: Sly Cupid will steal in at some little chink,
line_2: If you walk in the evening too late on the Link.

line_1: That drunk each night, and liquor'd ev'ry chink,
line_2: Dyes his red face in port, and his black soul in ink.

line_1: And azure eyes are seen through every chink.
line_2: Each to her oak the bashful Dryads shrink,

line_1: "While in yon chest my counted guineas chink,
line_2: " If still harmonious sounds mine ears may drink,
